description:
Title: Martyrs
Year: 2008
Country: Canada, France
Genre: Horror, Thriller, Drama
Duration: 1:39:00
Subtitles: Russian, English (switchable)

Director: Pascal Laugier

Cast: Al Allawi MORJANE (Morjana Alaoui), Milen Dzhampanoy (Mylene Jampanoi), Catherine Bedzhin (Catherine Begin), Robert Tupan (Robert Toupin), Patricia Tulasne (Patricia Tulasne), Juliette Gosselin (Juliette Gosselin), Xavier Dolan (Xavier Dolan), Isabelle Chasse (Isabelle Chasse), Emily Miskdzhyan (Emilie Miskdjian), Buffoon, Mike (Mike Chute), Gaell Cohen (Gaelle Cohen), Anna Pascal (Anie Pascale), Pam Jessie (Jessie Pham).

Fifteen years after a horrifying experience of abduction and prolonged torture, Lucie embarks on a bloody quest for revenge against her oppressors. Along with her childhood friend, Anna, who also suffered abuse, she quickly descends, without hope, into madness and her own delusions. Anna, left on her own begins to re-experience what Lucie did when she was only twelve years old.

